5 reads as rewritten:
6 "SECTION 4.(a) When the House of Representatives and the Senate adjourn on Thursday,
7 October 23, Friday, October 24, 2025, they stand adjourned to reconvene on Monday, November
8 17, 2025, at 10:00 A.M."
9 SECTION 2. This resolution is effective upon ratification.
